00:05:22.900 --> 00:05:24.785 align:middle line:10%
But, obviously, it's not random.

00:05:24.785 --> 00:05:29.920 align:middle line:10%
I'm going to take that point
and connect it to the G,

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:33.610 align:middle line:10%
