00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:19.990 align:middle line:10%
This is a visual
representation of something

00:06:19.990 --> 00:06:23.200 align:middle line:10%
called Thales Theorem, named
after the Greek philosopher who

00:06:23.200 --> 00:06:27.370 align:middle line:10%
