Pythagoras's mentor.

00:06:27.370 --> 00:06:30.615 align:middle line:10%
But Thales is best known
as the first person

00:06:30.615 --> 00:06:32.740 align:middle line:10%
to measure the height of
the Great Pyramid of Giza,

00:06:32.740 --> 00:06:38.060 align:middle line:10%
