direction, E for east.

00:07:25.420 --> 00:07:29.620 align:middle line:84%
And it's a zero
horizontal baseline.

00:07:29.620 --> 00:07:33.640 align:middle line:84%
Now, if it's really about
measuring the Earth, perhaps

00:07:33.640 --> 00:07:36.610 align:middle line:84%
all these lines that
are radiating out

00:07:36.610 --> 00:07:40.510 align:middle line:84%
from this enormous G dot
drawing attention to itself that

00:07:40.510 --> 00:07:43.120 align:middle line:84%
