from it, maybe they

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:48.060 align:middle line:84%
are intended to be thought
of as lines of latitude.

00:07:48.060 --> 00:07:53.200 align:middle line:84%
If we measure this one,
it's 20 degrees exactly.

00:07:53.200 --> 00:07:55.270 align:middle line:84%
And this one below the
horizontal baseline

00:07:55.270 --> 00:07:58.030 align:middle line:90%
