structure of Euler's number

00:12:48.520 --> 00:12:53.170 align:middle line:90%
e, the ratio 1 to 1.718.

00:12:53.170 --> 00:12:57.130 align:middle line:90%
And so the cubit is e minus 1.

00:12:57.130 --> 00:13:01.240 align:middle line:84%
This is the relationship
between foot and cubit.

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:05.860 align:middle line:10%
